          q_en: "How did you define priorities in the 5-point plan presented to the partner? Was there anything you considered but decided not to include?",
          a_en: "I prioritized based on: immediate pain relief first (financial credit), then confidence restoration (root cause + fix), finally future prevention (canary releases + emergency channel). Considered but didn't include: 1) SLA rebates (would be admission of systematic problems), 2) Technical co-location (too expensive), 3) Joint incident response team (too complex for quick implementation). Kept plan focused on high-impact, achievable commitments that could be delivered rapidly. Success depended on under-promising and over-delivering."
